      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "A writ Of review was signed by\nJudge Huneke this morning in five\ncases where the Great Northern\nRailroad company has questioned\nthe right Of Justice Hinkle to as\nsess S. attorneys fees in each case\nwhere judgment was rendered for\nsmall sums against the company in\nfavor OF Ernest Sergeant, the as\nsignee of the claims Of a number of\nlaborers. On June IL Justice Hin\nkle rendered judgment and assess\ned 1856 costs in each case."
